txt.en: You have been tasked with defeating the Gate of Gath Uior from allies of the Iron Crown.
You have defeated Thrasir and secured the Gate of Gath Uior
Secure the Gate of Gath Uior

'I thank you for coming to our aid. Since the Rangers departed, we have been able to hold the Gate of Gath Uior. Recently it has been difficult with the Iron Crown renewing their efforts to expand out from Angmar. You have assisted us and that assistance will not be forgotten. May your travels be swift and safe, my friend.'
Secure the Gate of Gath Uior.
